org.commonreality.time.impl

Class NetworkedClock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.commonreality.time.impl.BasicClock
      • org.commonreality.time.impl.NetworkedClock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IClock

    public class NetworkedClock
extends BasicClock
    General networked clock support. The code to send the network message for a time request is generalized as a Consumer that accepts a double. When your network code receives an update message, call NetworkedClock.NetworkedAuthoritativeClock.timeChangeReceived(double). This requires reliable transport as the request is only sent once.
    Author:
    harrison
